func:
msg.url = "https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/timezone/json"
    + '?location='
    + msg.item.replace(' ', '-')
    + "/"
    + msg.subcategory
    + "?ad=offering&price-type=fixed&price="
    + msg.minimum
    + "__"
    + msg.maximum
    + "&a-vendre-par=ownr";
    
return msg;
